comments: Thompson (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Ross (ORL) and gives him room to avoid contact.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Fournier (ORL) and absorbs the contact.
Fournier (ORL) makes incidental contact to the arm of Thompson (GSW) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
LLS shows Ross (ORL) makes some contact with Jerebko (GSW) during the rebound but does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Augustin (ORL) engages with Curry (ORL) prior to the screen but he is able to move through contact.
Cousins (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Augustin (ORL) and absorbs the contact.
Ross (ORL) makes some contact with Jerebko (ORL) during the rebound but does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
LLB shows Augustin (ORL) makes contact with Curry (GSW) during the drive but he is able to defend through contact.
RAR shows Thompson (GSW) briefly grasps Ross (ORL) during the screen but he is able to move through contact.
RAR Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Augustin (ORL) and does not deliver contact.
Gordon (ORL) moves laterally into the path of Curry (GSW) on the drive and the contact affects his SQBR.
Augustin (ORL) engages with Curry (GSW) prior to the screen but does not affect his FOM.
Augustin (ORL) makes some contact with Cousins (GSW) during the screen but he is able to move through contact.
Jerebko (GSW) and Ross (ORL) briefly engage and separate while rebounding.
Vucevic (ORL) makes incidental contact to Cousins' (GSW) arm after he releases the shot.
Cousins (GSW) makes contact with Ross's (ORL) head during the rebound affecting his ability to gather the ball.
Cousins (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Augustin (ORL) and firms up on his shoulder but is able to move through contact.
Green (GSW) maintains a legal pivot foot.
Jerebko (GSW) slightly extends his arms against Ross (ORL) during the screen but he is able to move through contact.
Gordon (ORL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Curry (GSW) and firms up on his side but he is able to move through contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Vucevic (ORL) lifts his pivot foot.
Cousins (GSW) makes marginal contact to the body of Vucevic (ORL) during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
LLS shows Gordon (ORL) clamps Green's (GSW) arm during the rebound affecting his ability to retrieve the ball.
Green (GSW) makes incidental contact to the arm of Gordon (ORL) after the release that does not affect his play at the basket.
Curry (GSW) takes fewer than three steps after he has gathered the ball.
Jerebko (GSW) commits a take foul on Gordon (ORL).
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Fournier (ORL) and firms up on his shoulder but he is able to move through contact.
Iwundu (ORL) makes some contact with Curry (GSW) during the rebound but does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Curry (GSW) attempts to commit a take foul on Fournier (ORL) but contact is marginal and does not affect his SQBR.
